{"tid":520234,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[CLS]007製作人不排除未來找來女性演員主演的可能性","createTime":"2018-01-05T08:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T02:44:16.000Z","uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c9565804dbf86d22c6790cd011f21248fae69625","tid":520234,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"時間已經到了 2018 年，而第 25 部龐德電影進展到確定同樣由丹尼爾克雷格（Daniel Craig）主演，他先前也提到他屬意找來《異星入境》（Arrival）、《銀翼殺手2049》（Blade Runner 2049）的導演丹尼斯維勒納夫（Denis Villeneuve）執導。不過除此之外，日前在與 DailyMail 的訪談中，此系列的製作人芭芭拉布洛克利（Barbara Broccoli）被問到，未來是否能夠接受由女性演員演出 007 探員的角色，或是除了白人以外膚色的演員演出，芭芭拉表示不排除這些可能性。<br />\n<br />\n「這些電影都反映了當代的狀況，所以我們一直都在繼續往極限推進。一切都是有可能的，現在是丹尼爾克雷格演出，我也非常開心跟他合作，但誰知道未來帶來什麼可能性呢？」"},{"pid":"eb54333c431d046b4e11602351ed3b11c5aee77d","tid":520234,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:39:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f43602cd116f7ef24db98c3338879eeefea0a56","tid":520234,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:43:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f8915fbf514315af0dc82d7743fd34f7c01c8ba","tid":520234,"uid":56729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"下場請參考新捉鬼敢死隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e892ba6765ad4eb4020454be3132e622f6ba4a84","tid":520234,"uid":86587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:06:56.000Z","msg":"女doctor, 女007, 女ghostbuster, 女ocean eight<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 荷理活已淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58248a0c5a7df34bca274abe221ad435c9244833","tid":520234,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"英雌聯盟"},{"pid":"396c2112053a53ed725b862b0682f55c1182ee41","tid":520234,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"此回